{"type":"text","timestamp":1783915553511,"sessionID":"ses_0a65ac472ffeMi6luqm6mHU9Lf","part":{"id":"prt_f59a6f647001yqBQxX2fEJwfuL","messageID":"msg_f59a6cd7b001Bhmr5bgI3wrxhz","sessionID":"ses_0a65ac472ffeMi6luqm6mHU9Lf","type":"text","text":"The detached lineage override is recognized as the workflow’s single-lineage path. I am loading the remaining command-owned dispatch, reducer, synthesis, and executor contracts before creating the lineage packet; the parent review packet and target remain read-only.","time":{"start":1783915542087,"end":1783915553509},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0a39a121d4f1de4a016a54641618c4819193f91302c28f559b","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783915553571,"sessionID":"ses_0a65ac472ffeMi6luqm6mHU9Lf","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_kjAq3sTAUtR4vUFi1g0QmAxm","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/review.md","offset":1,"limit":1200},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/review.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: description: Autonomous deep-review loop: iterative code audit with convergence detection. Modes :auto, :confirm.\n3: argument-hint: \"<target> [:auto|:confirm] [--max-iterations=N] [--convergence=N] [--convergence-mode=default|off|sliding-window|divergent] [--lineage-timeout-hours=N] [--stop-policy=convergence|max-iterations] [--spec-folder=PATH] [--no-resource-map] [--restart|--lineage-mode=restart] [--executor=<type> --model=X --config-dir=PATH --reasoning-effort=LEVEL --service-tier=TIER --executor-timeout=SECONDS --iters=N --count=N --label=X ...] [--executors=<json>] [--concurrency=N] (:auto supports PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS: prompt-body block for non-interactive setup)\"\n4: allowed-tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Grep, Glob, Task, mcp__mk_spec_memory__memory_context, mcp__mk_spec_memory__memory_search, mcp__mk_code_index__code_graph_query, mcp__mk_code_index__code_graph_context\n5: ---\n6: \n7: # Deep Start Review Loop\n8: \n9: !`node .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/runtime/scripts/render-command-contract.cjs --command deep/review -- '$ARGUMENTS'`\n\n(End of file - total 9 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\ndescription: Autonomous deep-review loop: iterative code audit with convergence detection. Modes :auto, :confirm.\nargument-hint: \"<target> [:auto|:confirm] [--max-iterations=N] [--convergence=N] [--convergence-mode=default|off|sliding-window|divergent] [--lineage-timeout-hours=N] [--stop-policy=convergence|max-iterations] [--spec-folder=PAT