e performance budgets to hold a Webflow build to, and the anti-patterns that blow them.\n\n### When to Use\n\nUse this reference when implementing or troubleshooting performance budgets, anti-patterns & related.\n\n---\n\n## 2. PERFORMANCE BUDGETS\n\n**Target metrics:**\n- First Contentful Paint (FCP): <1.8s\n- Largest Contentful Paint (LCP): <2.5s\n- Time to Interactive (TTI): <3.8s","lineStart":18,"lineEnd":37,"totalLines":241,"truncated":true}},"title":".opencode/skills/sk-code/code-webflow/references/implementation/performance_patterns/budgets_and_anti_patterns.md","time":{"start":1783918550734,"end":1783918550736}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_072683c7e4594319016a546fd624dc8191804b3e9defd0fb97"}},"id":"prt_f59d4dec3001NdLgUxwuAndbB3","sessionID":"ses_0a65ac472ffeMi6luqm6mHU9Lf","messageID":"msg_f59d481bf0016YtA9aSM8gMTPt"}}
